\par }\pard \ltrpar\s20\qj \fi-11\li851\ri0\widctlpar\tx-2552\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin851\itap0\pararsid6620336 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7161886 (i) Men and women in the Forces. (Recent strikes have stimulated this).

\par 
\par (ii) Skilled workers, such as "a semiskilled man earning \'a310 in an R.O.F. and receiving, in addition, a billeting allowance, while a thoroughly qualified engineer receives \'a35. 15. 0 a week".
\par 
\par (iii) Agricultural labourers. Some voluntary harvest workers, having now acquired first-hand experience of the work of agricultural labourers, consider them to be much underpaid.
